name: TYR Maxfit - Women's
description: Designed for pool or outdoor training, the reliable fabric lasts better than standard swimwear, so the fit doesn’t sag and the colour won’t fade. It also provides 4-way stretch and UPF 50+ protection.Durafast© fabric is colour fast, and stands up to 200+ hours of use in chlorine pools.Supportive shoulder straps and medium neckline.Moderate cut leg provides coverage.
